## How to use it

| Action | What to observe |
|---|---|
| **Add widgets** to both panels | Both panels grow identically |
| **Remove widgets** from Buggy | "Leaked Refs" counter climbs, memory bar grows, ghost list shows detached-but-alive nodes |
| **Remove widgets** from Fixed | "Freed Refs" counter climbs, memory bar shrinks back, nothing lingers |
| **Add 5 → Remove all** repeatedly | Buggy memory grows monotonically; Fixed stays flat |

