        <li>The GC <em>is</em> working correctly</li>
        <li>It cannot collect objects that are still referenced</li>
        <li>Blaming the runtime wastes debugging time</li>
        <li>No browser patch or GC tuning will fix this</li>
        <li>The leak will grow without bound until the tab crashes</li>
      </ul>
