      <h3>✅ Right: "We're holding references we shouldn't"</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>Remove every event listener when the widget is destroyed</li>
        <li>Call <code>clearInterval</code> / <code>clearTimeout</code> on teardown</li>
        <li>Splice removed entries from any global registry/array</li>
        <li>Nullify closure variables that capture DOM nodes</li>
