          still holds a closure referencing the widget's data object. The GC sees live references
          and correctly keeps everything in memory. The leak is the references, not the GC.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="truth-card wrong">
        <h4>❌ Why "force GC" won't fix it</h4>
        <p>
