          find the same live references and collect nothing. Forcing GC on a real leak
          is like emptying a bucket while the tap is still running. You must close the tap —
          remove the references — first.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="truth-card right">
        <h4>✅ The actual fix</h4>
