          Before removing a widget: call removeEventListener with the exact same function
          reference, clear all intervals/timers, null out or splice the DOM reference from
          the tracking array. Now the GC sees zero references to the widget objects and
          collects them on the very next cycle. The GC was never broken.
        </p>
      </div>
